          <lg><l>Dulce solamen miseris ministrans </l><lb/>
            <l>Horridam pestem famis amputauit, </l><lb/>
            <l>Barbara plures feritate uictos </l><lb/>
            <l>Soluit ab hoste. </l></lg>
          <lg><l>Magne confessor, humilis magister, </l><lb n="5"/>
            <l>Tu quidem normam monachis dedisti, </l><lb/>
            <l>Calle demonstrans sobrio sequaces </l><lb/>
            <l>Scandere caelum. </l></lg>
          <lg><l>In tuis sanctis manibus refulsit </l><lb/>
            <l>Caelitus lumen refluensque creuit </l><lb n="10"/>
            <l>Ad tuos haustus olei liquamen </l><lb/>
            <l>Fontis ad instar. </l></lg>
          <lg><l>Condolens cunctos inopes fouebat, </l><lb/>
            <l>Languidos <choice><sic>Banans</sic><corr>sanans</corr></choice> releuabat aegros: </l><lb/>
            <l>Omnis accedens salubrem medelam </l><lb n="15"/>
            <l>Sumpsit ab illo. </l></lg>
          <lg><l>Tuque Siluinum loculo iacentem, </l><lb/>
            <l>Fratribus coram <choice><sic>preoibus</sic><corr>precibus</corr></choice> peractis, </l><lb/>
            <l>Morte deuicta redire fecisti ad </l><lb/>
            <l>Gaudia uitae. </l><lb n="20"/>
            </lg>
          <lg><l>Cereos flamma fidei cremante </l><lb/>
            <l>Arguit sanctus pater infideles: </l><lb/>
            <l>Moxque flammescunt deitatis igne </l><lb/>
            <l>Algida corda. </l></lg>

